## 1. Where Middleman Sits In The 3‑Company Stack

Think in terms of layers:

- StreetCode (TapIDE)
  - Where devs and founders “make tracks” (agents, workflows, tools).
  - Every run, test, deploy hits APIs for models, tools, and infra.
- BlackMind
  - Heavy models, CRISPR‑style agent editing, deep inference spend.
